2:T73e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Steve AI better than Synthesia?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Steve AI scores 6.0 overall while Synthesia scores 8.0. Steve AI is best for animated explainer videos and educational content, while Synthesia excels for corporate training videos and multilingual business content."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Steve AI or Synthesia?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Steve AI starts at $20/mo and Synthesia starts at $22/mo. Steve AI offers a free plan. Synthesia offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Steve AI to Synthesia?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Steve AI and Synthesia support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Steve AI vs Synthesia?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Steve AI holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Synthesia has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Steve AI for good animation styles and Synthesia for 160+ realistic ai avatars."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Steve AI or Synthesia?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Synthesia for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Steve AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize good animation styles. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInne